results.name: Decimal expansion of sum(1/(k^(phi(k)), k=1..infinity), where phi(n) is the Euler totient function.
maple: with(numtheory); P:=proc(q) local k; print(evalf(add(1/k^phi(k),k=1..q),100)); end: P(1000);
results.author: _Paolo P. Lava_, Mar 25 2014
